	<Name>3x3 Eyes - Seima Kourinden (Japan)</Name>
	<plot>Overview:3x3 Eyes: Seima Kourinden is a role-playing game developed and published by Yutaka for the SNES platform. 3x3 Eyes: Seima Kourinden was only released in Japan and is based on the manga series 3x3 Eyes, concerning a magical three-eyed girl and her immortal champion. The game was followed up with another Super Famicom 3x3 Eyes game, 3x3 Eyes: Juuma Houkan.Gameplay:3x3 Eyes: Seima Kourin Den is a traditional turn based Japanese role-playing game.	</plot>
